{"tid":280582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15:30更新: 天文台預計今天下午5時30分前發八號 路程偏遠市民現應啟程回家","createTime":"2017-06-12T07:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T07:02:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58e3a65ad50dffd35cc30d5aec69fd1c44b6c036","tid":280582,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"熱帶氣旋之特別報告\t15:30 更新<br />\n香港天文台宣布預計在今天（6月12日）下午5時30分或以前發出八號熱帶氣旋警告信號，本港風勢將會加強。<br />\n<br />\n政府提醒返家路程偏遠、轉折或居住離島的市民，現應啟程回家。政府已通知屬下此類員工下班。<br />\n<br />\n教育局宣布：所有學校今日停課。學校應實施應變措施，確保學生安全，並在安全情況下，安排學生返家。"},{"pid":"e6c4902fbc0a8ac21137487443e7ca9ebd6a7912","tid":280582,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:41:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/contentc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fcontentc.htm&d=R6ovdL9rzY5bByH2AfPvFk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=260d85cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/contentc.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8cc325a9d91c88cdd08715009c025bc24c8fb54f","tid":280582,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20130814/large/1376448407_d67f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130814%2Flarge%2F1376448407_d67f.jpg&h=9e9c2375&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"121f6aa5ccbe9c345b56f47d87ad3d88d0ce4603","tid":280582,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"咁都有負皮??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290526d69c33f13ae992198cdd3a7e6f3274f717","tid":280582,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:44:33.000Z","msg":"5點29分掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9763e725c0b983e0e5852be17afa09819187f46f","tid":280582,"uid":10098